### Tabs

<Tabs value={activeTab} onChange={setActiveTab}>
  <Tabs.List>
    <Tabs.Tab value='details'>Details</Tabs.Tab>
  </Tabs.List>

  <Tabs.Panels>
    <Tabs.Panel value='details'>Details content…</Tabs.Panel>
  </Tabs.Panels>
</Tabs>

Tabs – root, manages state & context
Tabs.List – wrapper for the tab buttons (renders a <div role='tablist'>)
Tabs.Tab – the clickable “button” (renders <button role='tab'>)
Tabs.Panels – wrapper for all panels
Tabs.Panel – content area (renders <div role='tabpanel'>)

I also want the tab components driven by a json object as well as jsx

